# MeetMaker Design (Material 3)

## Audience
Women 18–35 inviting someone on a date or cozy meetup. Warm Russian copy.

## Visual
- **System**: Material Design 3 dark — Roboto, surface `#141218`, elevated cards `#2B2930`
- **Themes**: romantic (pink), coffee (orange), minimal (violet) — use `[data-theme]` CSS tokens
- **Components**: `PostcardFrame` (elevated card + accent bar), `md-filled-button`, `md-list-item`
- **Never**: flat black-only UI, harsh indigo, Framer `initial={{ opacity: 0 }}`

## Motion (M3 emphasized easing `cubic-bezier(0.2, 0, 0, 1)`)
- Step changes: `md-reveal` / `StepTransition`
- Success: `ConfettiBurst`, `md-celebrate-ring`, `md-success-pop`
- Cards: `md-card-enter` on `PostcardFrame`
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`

## Copy
- Prefer «приглашение», «открытка», «встреча» — not «сессия», «данные»
